{
  "stem": "1502.6",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What we found outside was maybe a number-- maybe 100 to 200 people, Belgians, with-- with the sacks to loot-- to loot from the camp if there was anything to loot there.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What was there to loot from these poor Jews?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, that's only a detail.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We walked out of the camp, and we started to walk in the streets.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As we walked out from camp, we did-- there was a Jewish committee came already from Brussels.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And because we had no money, and they gave everybody 1,000 or 2,000 francs so we should have money to take a bus, or a train or whatever.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were no buses, there were no trains, there was nothing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Walked out in the streets, there were no Germans and there were no Allies.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was nobody.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The underground was running in the streets.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "During the war, you couldn't see much of them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But once the Germans were gone, everybody became underground.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They all put on bands say underground.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "All had their rifles, and their running from cars, looking for Germans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Through the war, we saw very little of them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we-- we walked in the streets for a few hours.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Not too long, I think was like 10 o'clock, and people started to scream that the British-- [INAUDIBLE]-- [PAUSES FOR 14 SECONDS] That the British are there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Not to block their way, they are British.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we were in-- a block away, and we saw the British.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We saw the British tanks, was a column of tanks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we-- we stopped the tanks, and we told them that they liberated a camp with 500 Jews.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They say, oh, very interesting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We're going to-- we're going to call headquarters, and we go and tell them over the radio.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But we-- we kissed the tanks.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
